Sentencas: Mixed transition-metal oxide Ni0.79Co0.2Zn0.01O (NCZ) powders have been prepared by the modified Pechini method and studied as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: A novel composite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The Ni-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9(SDC)vertical bar SDC ' SDC-NCZ single cell achieves 326 mW cm(-2) at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: A novel composite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The output power has been further improved by partial substituting Li for Ni at Ni sites.
Titulo: A novel composite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The Ni-SDC vertical bar SDC vertical bar SDC-Li0.2Ni0.79Co0.2Zn0.01O2 (L(2)NCZ) cell with the SDC film of 30 mu m in thickness shows maximum power outputs of 1.32, 0.98 and 0.62 W cm(-2) at 650, 600 and 550 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: A novel composite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The impedance measurements at open circuit conditions show that the overall electrode polarization resistances is 0.033, 0.112, 0351 Omega cm(2) at 650, 600 and 550 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: A novel composite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The primary results indicate a new family of potential cathode material compatible with the SDC electrolyte for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: A novel composite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell
